comments: This teacher is very entertaining but can offend some people. He uses affective examples to teach social problems. Great professor if you have an open mind and don\'t get easily offened. Easy tests little to no semester work but has a long 10page paper.
Fun teacher kept the classes interesting. A little unorganized. Beware of his in class tests those are tough.

i believe he is a very good teacher, he is very knowledgeable in his field and brings real life situations/scenarios into his teaching. he is also a fun teacher and tries to make class interesting and appealing to students.

He knows what he is talking about, and his classes are fun. He is a little unorganized-which when he does things like pull questions from the wrong text book for the test- can be a little panic inducing, but he admits his mistakes and makes up for them.
